<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-40-0426 </DOCNO><TEXT>A compilation of the results of a survey held amongst the Dutch gas industriesby VEGIN (Association of Owners of Gas Industries in the Netherlands)to the period 1981 to 1986 is presented. Data are given on the gas salesand the connections to the gas mains for different sectors: small-scaleand large-scale consumption, district heating and market gardening. Alsodata are given on gas prices, financial management, and financial-economicaland distribution-technical data of the gas companies. Finally data aregiven of gas sales and the number of connections to the gas mains perprovince in the Netherlands for the year 1986.</TEXT></DOC>